{"title":"伟大的一日","authors":["王亚平"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":10,"day":3}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"伟大的一日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一、人民的广场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"数不清的国旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎着风活活地飘扬；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的京城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变成了红色的海洋。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二、天安门上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八只红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"八只宫灯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高悬在天安门上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣布人民共和国成立，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巨大的声音"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激荡在每个人的心里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三、国旗上升"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万人的心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随着国旗上升。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢喜的泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"充溢了二十万人的眼睛。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国旗升到高空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十万人的脸上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"立刻浮起了骄傲的笑容。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四、礼炮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象春雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十四响礼炮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国革命胜利了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民大团结，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信心比天高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它，庄严地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向世界宣告！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五、阅兵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年青的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明晃晃的刺刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会场中间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰过了装甲兵团，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红马队，白马队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马背上，——稳坐着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的英豪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民的飞机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"展开翅膀飞绕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常胜的队伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比钢铁还强，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们接受了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东思想。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六、示威、游行！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十万人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"分向了西城，东城；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二十万只火把、灯笼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了市街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照亮了星斗点点的夜空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国的人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一次为了自己的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了祖国的新生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排开无尽的队伍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平大示威！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"壮丽的游行！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"１９４９，１０，１，北京"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}